            <div class="info-cards">
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h3>Alumni Reunion 2025</h3>
                    <p>Save the date for our annual reunion happening on June 15-17, 2025. Early registration opens next month!</p>
                    <div class="info-meta">
                        <span class="date">May 10, 2025</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h3>New Mentorship Program</h3>
                    <p>We're launching a revamped mentorship program connecting current students with successful alumni in their fields.</p>
                    <div class="info-meta">
                        <span class="date">May 5, 2025</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h3>Summer Workshops</h3>
                    <p>Registration is now open for our professional development summer workshops series. Limited spots available!</p>
                    <div class="info-meta">
                        <span class="date">April 28, 2025</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
